	abstract = {Introduction: Walking has the potential to promote health across the life span, but age-specific features of the neighborhood environment ({NE}), especially in rural communities, linked with walking have not been adequately characterized. This study examines the relationships between {NE} and utilitarian walking among older vs. younger adults living in {US} rural towns.
